{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9b25eda626","title":"同苏修大使契尔沃年科的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8a75038c8a","index":0,"year":1963,"month":2,"day":23,"articleId":"9b25eda626"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a47768ba43","type":"title","text":"同苏修大使契尔沃年科的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"9b25eda626"},{"id":"eb6bef9e05","type":"paragraph","text":"（苏修大使契尔沃年科求见主席，主席称不适。因再三要求，主席着睡衣接见。）","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"9b25eda626"},{"id":"f9dc4b7aa6","type":"paragraph","text":"契：听说你们要发表文章，不必要的，感到很沉重。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"9b25eda626"},{"id":"27cd842eff","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：不必要，你们为什么发表那么多文章？没有什么沉重的，不过互相论战，不过是唇枪舌箭而已。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"9b25eda626"},{"id":"9cea0ee7a3","type":"paragraph","text":"契：请你到莫斯科去谈一谈，可以吗？","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"9b25eda626"},{"id":"7e4c816843","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我已经老了，不中用了。老而不死，破套鞋去不成了。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"9b25eda626"}],"page":{"id":"071b47c35d","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"9b25eda626","start":87,"end":87}}}},"__N_SSG":true}